'''牛奶河'''（{{lang-en|Milk River}}）位於[[美國|美國]][[蒙大拿州|蒙大拿州]]及[[加拿大|加拿大]][[亞伯達省|亞伯達省]]，長約{{convert|729|mi|km}}，是[[密蘇里河|密蘇里河]]其中一條支流<ref name="Canadian Encyclopedia"/>。牛奶河發源於[[洛磯山脈|洛磯山脈]]，河流流量偏低。它先後兩度流經美加邊界，最終在蒙大拿州的[[佩克堡_(蒙大拿州)|佩克堡]]以東與密蘇里河匯合<ref name="Water-Data Report"/>。

牛奶河的流域包括美國蒙大拿州、加拿大亞伯達省及[[薩斯喀徹溫省|薩斯喀徹溫省]]。根據加拿大牛奶河流域委員會（Milk River Watershed Council Canada）的數據，牛奶河的流域面積為23,800平方英里（61,642平方公里），其中2,510平方英里（6,500平方公里）位於亞伯達省，5,769平方英里（14,942平方公里）位於薩斯喀徹溫省，其餘15,521平方英里（40,199平方公里）則位於蒙大拿州<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.mrwcc.ca/index.php/watershed/overview-milk-river-watershed/ |title = Milk River Watershed |author = Milk River Watershed Council Canada |language = en |accessdate = 2020-07-26 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191130232940/http://www.mrwcc.ca/index.php/watershed/overview-milk-river-watershed/ |archivedate = 2019-11-30}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
牛奶河由[[路易斯與克拉克遠征|路易斯與克拉克遠征]]的其中一名領隊、[[美國|美國]][[探險家|探險家]][[梅里韋瑟·路易斯|梅里韋瑟·路易斯]]所命名，而他在日記內這樣寫道<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://lewisandclarkjournals.unl.edu/read/?_xmlsrc=1805-05-08.xml&_xslsrc=LCstyles.xsl |title = The Journals of the Lewis and Clark Expedition |author = Meriwether Lewis |date = 1805-05-08 |publisher = University of Nebraska |language = en |accessdate = 2020-07-05 |archive-date = 2016-06-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160617114627/http://lewisandclarkjournals.unl.edu/read/?_xmlsrc=1805-05-08.xml&_xslsrc=LCstyles.xsl |dead-url = no }}</ref>：

{{quote|這條河的河水有著奇特的白色，大概是一杯茶和一湯匙牛奶混合後的的顏色。從河水的顏色，我們稱之為牛奶河。{{notetag|1=原文為「the water of this river possesses a peculiar whiteness, being about the colour of a cup of tea with the admixture of a tablespoonfull of milk. from the colour of its water we called it Milk river.」}}}}

河水的白色外觀是由水中懸浮的粘土和淤泥引起的。亞伯達省南部牛奶河流域沿岸有著不同的地層組，例如是{{tsl|en|Foremost Formation|福莫斯特組}}、{{tsl|en|Oldman Formation|老人組}}及[[恐龍公園組|恐龍公園組]]，而這些富含軟粘土的岩石因[[侵蝕作用|侵蝕作用]]而變成細顆粒狀的沉積物，並堆積在河內<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://ags.aer.ca/publications/MAP_600.html |title = Bedrock Geology of Alberta |last = Prior |first = G.J. |last2 = Hathway |first2 = B. |last3 = Glombick |first3 = P.M. |last4 = Pana |first4 = D.I. |last5 = Banks |first5 = C.J. |last6 = Hay |first6 = D.C. |last7 = Schneider |first7 = C.L. |last8 = Grobe |first8 = M. |last9 = Elgr |first9 = R. |last10 = Weiss |first10 = J.A. |date = 2013-06-17 |publisher = Alberta Geological Survey |language = en |accessdate = 2020-07-25 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130926020425/http://www.ags.gov.ab.ca/publications/MAP/PDF/MAP_600.pdf |archivedate = 2013-09-26}}</ref>。

在[[路易斯安那購地|路易斯安那購地]]後、路易斯等人前往當地考察時，牛奶河流域早已合法地屬於美國{{sfn|Saindon|2003|pp=213-215}}。但是[[1818年條約|在1818年美英兩國所簽署的條約]]內，美國的談判代表以北緯49度以北的一部分牛奶河流域，向英方交換當時屬於[[英屬北美|英屬北美]]的一部分[[红河_(温尼伯湖)|雷德河]]流域{{sfn|Saindon|2003|pp=213-215}}。

1908年，為了澄清[[印第安保留地|印第安保留地]]的[[水權|水權]]問題，牛奶河的水域成為了[[美國最高法院|美國最高法院]]其中一宗案件，此案後來被稱為{{tsl|en|Winters v. United States|溫特斯訴美國案}}（207 U.S. 564 (1908)）{{sfn|Duthu|2008|p=105}}。

== 流向 ==
牛奶河發源於[[蒙大拿州|蒙大拿州]][[冰川縣_(蒙大拿州)|冰川縣]]附近的牛奶河南汊及中汊的匯合處<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.allglacier.com/lakes_rivers_falls/milk_river.php |title = Milk River |author = AllTrips Glacier National Park |language = en |accessdate = 2020-07-26 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200726092543/https://www.allglacier.com/lakes_rivers_falls/milk_river.php |archivedate = 2020-07-26}}</ref>。而這兩條分別長約{{convert|30|mi|km}}及{{convert|20|mi|km}}的南汊及中汊則是發源於[[洛磯山脈|洛磯山脈]]，在[[冰川國家公園_(美國)|冰川國家公園]]以東、{{tsl|en|Blackfeet Nation|黑腳印地安保留區}}內<ref name="USBR Report 2012">{{Cite web |url = https://www.usbr.gov/watersmart/bsp/docs/finalreport/Milk-StMary/Milk-StMary_SummaryReport.pdf |title = St. Mary River and Milk River Basins Study Summary Report |author = Milk River Project, Montana |year = 2012 |publisher = U.S. Bureau of Reclamation |language = en |accessdate = 2020-07-26 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200627221836/https://www.usbr.gov/watersmart/bsp/docs/finalreport/Milk-StMary/Milk-StMary_SummaryReport.pdf |archivedate = 2020-06-27}}</ref>。河水會往東北方向東流入加拿大的[[亞伯達省|亞伯達省]]南部，並與牛奶河的北部支流匯合，然後流經{{tsl|en|Milk River, Alberta|米爾克里弗}}及{{tsl|en|Writing-on-Stone Provincial Park|省立石刻公園}}<ref name="USBR Report 2012"/>。河水其後會往東南方流動，跨越[[美加邊界|美加邊界]]後再度流入蒙大拿州，並流經{{tsl|en|Fresno Dam|弗雷斯諾水壩}}、[[哈佛_(蒙大拿州)|哈佛]]及{{tsl|en|Fort Belknap Indian Reservation|貝克那城堡印地安保留區}}的北部，最終在佩克堡以東與[[密蘇里河|密蘇里河]]合流<ref name="Water-Data Report"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.usbr.gov/projects/pdf.php?id=136 |title = Milk River Project |last = Simonds |first = Wm. Joe |year = 1998 |publisher = U.S. Bureau of Reclamation |language = en |accessdate = 2020-07-26 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190928212908/https://www.usbr.gov/projects/pdf.php?id=136 |archivedate = 2019-09-28}}</ref><ref name="IJC"/><ref name="NY Times"/>。

== 流量 ==
牛奶河的河流流量主要取決於春季融雪和附近山麓丘陵地區的降雨量，因此在作為水源時不如鄰近的{{tsl|en|St. Mary River (Alberta–Montana)|聖瑪麗河}}可靠<ref name="IJC">{{Cite web |url = https://www.ijc.org/en/watersheds/oldman-milk-rivers |title = St. Mary and Milk Rivers |author = International Joint Commission |language = en |accessdate = 2020-07-26 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181204175110/https://www.ijc.org/en/watersheds/oldman-milk-rivers |archivedate = 2018-12-04}}</ref>。為了穩定水流量，美國政府在1917年興建了聖瑪麗運河，並利用虹吸管把水由聖瑪麗河引流至牛奶河的北汊。另外，美國和加拿大根據1909年簽訂的《{{tsl|en|Boundary Waters Treaty of 1909|英（加）美邊界水資源條約}}》成立了[[國際聯合委員會|國際聯合委員會]]，而委員會則按照該條約及1921年通過的IJC命令，為聖瑪麗河和牛奶河流域的河水的測量和分配工作提供指導<ref name="IJC"/><ref name="IJC Report 2013">{{Cite web |url = https://ijc.org/sites/default/files/AOSMMR-2013-Report.PDF |title = Report to THE INTERNATIONAL JOINT COMMISSIONOnTHE DIVISION OF THE WATERS OFTHE ST. MARY AND MILK RIVERS 2013 |last = Ethridge |first = Max M. |last2 = Pietroniro |first2 = Alain |date = 2014-01-01 |publisher = International Joint Commission |language = en |accessdate = 2020-07-26 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200726110600/https://www.ijc.org/sites/default/files/AOSMMR-2013-Report.PDF |archivedate = 2020-07-26}}</ref>。

2020年5月，聖瑪麗運河發生坍塌，切斷了流向加拿大部分地區和蒙大納州東部大部分地區的農場和城鎮的河水供應<ref name="Global News">{{Cite web |url = https://globalnews.ca/news/7093397/st-mary-canal-repairs-milk-river-water-shortages/ |title = Water shortages expected on Alberta’s Milk River as repairs begin on Montana canal |last = Knight |first = Demi |date = 2020-06-22 |publisher = Global News |language = en |accessdate = 2020-07-26 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200623083756/https://globalnews.ca/news/7093397/st-mary-canal-repairs-milk-river-water-shortages/ |archivedate = 2020-06-23}}</ref><ref name="NY Times">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/14/us/montana-water-milk-river.html |title = A Canal That Opened the Montana Prairie May Soon Dry Up |last = Robbins |first = Jim |date = 2020-06-15 |publisher = The New York Times)|language = en |accessdate = 2020-07-26 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200614145003/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/14/us/montana-water-milk-river.html |archivedate = 2020-06-14}}</ref>。蒙大拿州政府官員表示，他們也許能夠在秋天之前完成修復工作，但在此之前居民需要節約用水<ref name="Global News"/><ref name="NY Times"/>。鑑於結構倒塌，亞伯達省向米爾克里弗提供了額外的資金，以增加該鎮的儲水量<ref name="Global News"/>。

